column16: Johnny Giavotella grounds into a force out, shortstop Alcides Escobar to second baseman Raul Mondesi.   Carlos Perez out at 2nd.
Danny Worth grounds out, shortstop Alcides Escobar to first baseman Eric Hosmer.
George Springer pops out to third baseman Cheslor Cuthbert in foul territory.
Jason Castro doubles (8) on a line drive to right fielder Paulo Orlando.   Jake Marisnick scores.    Luis Valbuena to 3rd.
